<title>ITALY: IBCA affirms BCI sht term rate A1 plus.</title>
<headline>IBCA affirms BCI sht term rate A1 plus.</headline>
<dateline>MILAN 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>European credit rating agency IBCA said it affirmed Banca Commerciale Italiana's ratings at a short-term A1-plus and a long term of AA minus.</p>
<p>In a statement received in Milan IBCA said it also affirmed BCI at an Individual of B/C and legal of 2.</p>
</text>
